-- DESIGNER: Terry Kang, Tim Makimov 
--
-- PROGRAMMER: Terry Kang, Tim Makimov 
--
-- NOTES:
-- This program is a  GPS applications on Embedded platforms Raspberry Pi
--
-- The program will retrieve data from GPS and displays the data on console mode.
-- There are 2 different version that can be switched using command argument '-c' or '-h'
-- '-c' mode will print only basic data with plain console UI.
-- '-h' mode will print more data with graphical console UI using ncurses.
--
-- this program requires GPS dongle to be connected to the device.
-- Since this program connect the GPS dongle via gps daemon(gpsd), gpsd must be installed and running.
--
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/